Description: Portable USB creator for open.Yellow.os
 Create BIOS/UEFI portable live USB media with persistence for open.Yellow.os.
 This package installs the GUI launcher, CLI engine, helper libraries,
 templates, desktop integration, icon, and PolicyKit action.
